Albee Layer, who's a
big wave surfer as well

00:39:07.420 --> 00:39:09.130
who's about 20 years younger.

00:39:09.130 --> 00:39:12.460
The whole idea behind
getting these two guys

00:39:12.460 --> 00:39:13.930
together was longevity.

00:39:13.930 --> 00:39:16.645
You know, there's one
thing to go out and catch

00:39:16.645 --> 00:39:18.102
a 50-foot wave once or twice.

00:39:18.102 --> 00:39:19.810
It's another thing to
do it for 30 years.

00:39:19.810 --> 00:39:21.910
Shane Dorian's done
that for 30 years.

00:39:21.910 --> 00:39:23.830
He's proven that time, safety--

00:39:23.830 --> 00:39:27.790
he's invented that
inflation system.

00:39:27.790 --> 00:39:29.590
So if you're underwater,
you pull a cord,

00:39:29.590 --> 00:39:32.260
and you have two CO2
cartridges that inflate,

00:39:32.260 --> 00:39:33.760
so you float to the surface.

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:36.970
Fortunately-- well,
unfortunately, he

00:39:36.970 --> 00:39:38.620
had a situation that
made him do that,

00:39:38.620 --> 00:39:40.450
and it made him think
about his two kids, which

00:39:40.450 --> 00:39:42.866
is a terrible situation that
happened up in Half Moon Bay,

00:39:42.866 --> 00:39:43.960
but he was OK.

00:39:43.960 --> 00:39:46.000
Ever since then, he had
a two-wave hold down.

00:39:46.000 --> 00:39:46.510
Came up.

00:39:46.510 --> 00:39:47.710
Could barely breathe.

00:39:47.710 --> 00:39:51.640
And since then, he's saved a
lot of lives with his invention.

00:39:51.640 --> 00:39:54.610
So when I say these
images are a part of us,

00:39:54.610 --> 00:39:57.670
it's a part of our creation,
also part of what we're doing

00:39:57.670 --> 00:39:59.930
is we're sharing these stories
to inform about safety.

